de.bfs.radon.omsimulation.data

Class OMSimulation

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.bfs.radon.omsimulation.data.OMSimulation

  • public class OMSimulation
extends java.lang.Object
    Public class OMSimulation used for creating simulation meta-objects with custom name and all the campaigns used for analysis later. OMS simulation files are DB4O databases of this type!
    Author:
    A. Schoedon
